- Para los datos del perfil, o para la seccion settings: https://tailwindui.com/components/application-ui/data-display/description-lists - https://tailwindui.com/components/application-ui/forms/form-layouts

- Para ofrecer opciones de suscripcion o de pago en algo de la app: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/pricing
 
- Footers para contactos: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/newsletter-sections

- Mostras datos Numericos o estadisticas: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/stats-sections

- Testimonios de Usuarios: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/testimonials

- Mostrar Opiniones de suarios: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/blog-sections

- Seccion acerca de nosotros: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/content-sections

- Footers con Logo: https://tailwindui.com/components/marketing/sections/logo-clouds

